{"tid":1403092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱同老母傾完計，關於依場運動","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:49:18.000Z","uid":130046,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc6d6e4316a5f5b37365e6421d06839af876560","tid":1403092,"uid":130046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:44:13.000Z","msg":"佢話遊行示威已經make 左好多noise<br />\n甚至shock到上一輩<br />\n有人選擇做港豬，有人選擇去危言聳聽，有人選擇去守護我哋嘅核心價值<br />\n<br />\n佢哋已經表左軚，示威遊行已經達到佢哋嘅目的，亦都引起國際嘅關注<br />\n<br />\n而我哋繼續落去咁樣示威只會好似細路仔發爛渣一樣咁肉酸。<br />\n<br />\n我哋支持行動，勇武嘅應該代替警察維持治安。<br />\n<br />\n行動 - 除咗衝擊之外有好多方向，渣哥就係一個好例子<br />\n<br />\n佢唔罷工，佢謹守崗位，叫人寫一張香港人加油嘅memo紙就送嘢食。變相幫我地宣傳去關注我哋嘅運動<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住我哋嘅目的，無論係想港獨，民主回歸，定係焦土。<br />\n<br />\n都要記住點解我哋要咁做：<br />\n<br />\n係因為我哋嘅核心價值同支那唔一樣<br />\n<br />\n我哋要嘅係<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主 法治 自由</strong><br />\n<br />\n記得記得宣揚比其他人，尤其是下一代嘅教育<br />\n<br />\n香港人 我愛你<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UE72Hpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUE72Hpd.png&h=12f13c18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6P4kt4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6P4kt4e.png&h=02138251&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVppbhB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVppbhB.png&h=460cf909&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayUTO4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FayUTO4h.png&h=774d51b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpfS4CE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpfS4CE.png&h=0d743634&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUu4VKk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUu4VKk.png&h=0f70c821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a30a4ee77be5f393f51bbbf96197deacf1e2934","tid":1403092,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":